extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div
      h1.text-shadow Hello, Potential Employers 
      p.lead.text-light
        | This is what I consider my online/living resume. It's purpose is to highlight the projects that I am completing on treehouse. Enjoy!
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3 
      each project in projects
        .cell
          a(href=`/project/${project.id}`)
            img.effect.thumbnail(src=project.image_urls[0])
            h5= `${project.project_name}`